metadata.description: Juggernaut #1 is the very first trial custom motorcycle from Mutant, combining different materials and styles: its origin combines scrambler, street fighter, Mars rover and a pinch of skateboard genes. Its unique signature is the left side tank "opening" where its "mechanical veins" can be seen. [TETHER VIN:JYARJ18Y7CA002178]
metadata.name: Juggernaut #1
